data.description: The ''Huger Model'' is an easy living one level cottage plan.  This home is being planned for completion in August of 2022, so now is the time to pick your colors and selections! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath plan has an open living and dining area, with a stylish kitchen offering 42'' hardwood kitchen cabinets and granite countertops.  This home will have hardwood floors throughout, with  18'' ceramic tile floors in the baths.  This home also has an attached garage and community amenities that includes a swimming pool. This country setting, close to Mount Pleasant, offers all the value and amenities in a new home.
